{"id":252792,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/维权网-福州警察继续软禁维权人士林应强（图）/","date":"2012-09-19T18:15:54Z","modified":"2012-09-19T18:15:54Z","title":"维权网 | 福州警察继续软禁维权人士林应强（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员任长霞报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>·</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>事变纪念日，福州冤民林应强在家门口被福州警察和维稳官员等十几个人抓上车，非法囚禁在福州仓山区盖山镇政府一整天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日早上，福州冤民林应强准备出门去超市买菜，没想到和昨日一样被几个盖山派出所警察和维稳官员堵在门口不让外出。警察说是因外面还在保钓游行，怕你外出保钓或去告发腐败，奉上级命令才限制你外出。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>林应强据理力争，要求警察出示限制他人身自由的有关法律文书，竟遭拒绝。愤怒的他当即向福州市公安局</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警，可仓山分局仓前派出所的警察（警号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">101465</span><span>）接警后，却未作任何处置。对于林应强的质疑，仅是丢下一句话：你不要难为我，不服可以去告！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>林应强一向嫉恶如仇，一直在告发福州腐败村长张文灿犯罪行径。只因腐败村长张文灿在福州一手遮天，其腐败行径被揭后，疯狂报复林应强。为此，林应强共</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>次被暴力追杀致伤，被坐牢，被拘留，被囚禁，被失业。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>林应强现在被禁止外出，不让去保钓，不让去伸冤，不让去告发腐败，不让去陪护年老多病已</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">81</span><span>高龄的老父亲，更不让去超市买菜或去找工作谋生。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>不管林应强外出是去保钓，或是去告发腐败村长张文灿，应该都是政府大力提倡的正义行为。林应强不禁要问：盖山派出所警察为什么不让他去保钓，上前线抛洒热血，保疆卫土？同样，不让他去告发腐败，岂不等同于警察是和腐败分子沆瀣一气！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4BxuZc-raVA/UFn1n89gDzI/AAAAAAAAO-c/wgJ7DLeQFnk/s1600/%E8%BD%AF%E7%A6%811.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4BxuZc-raVA/UFn1n89gDzI/AAAAAAAAO-c/wgJ7DLeQFnk/s320/%E8%BD%AF%E7%A6%811.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-gdh8hNyumcY/UFn1pQ0BB4I/AAAAAAAAO-k/UNznEE2q1qo/s1600/%E8%BD%AF%E7%A6%812.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"229\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-gdh8hNyumcY/UFn1pQ0BB4I/AAAAAAAAO-k/UNznEE2q1qo/s320/%E8%BD%AF%E7%A6%812.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-CFLpHgJju7A/UFn1q5lmEmI/AAAAAAAAO-s/i9YMeEfsLAo/s1600/%E8%BD%AF%E7%A6%813.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"210\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-CFLpHgJju7A/UFn1q5lmEmI/AAAAAAAAO-s/i9YMeEfsLAo/s320/%E8%BD%AF%E7%A6%813.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7102308300189066172?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}